name: timm

scripts.build: yarn lint && yarn flow && yarn compile && yarn uglify && yarn testCovFull && yarn docs && yarn xxl
scripts.compile: rm -rf ./lib && mkdir lib && babel -o lib/timm.js src/timm.js && cp src/api.js.flow lib/timm.js.flow && cp src/timm.d.ts lib/timm.d.ts
scripts.testCovFast: yarn testCovPrepare && yarn testCovDev && yarn testCovReport
scripts.testCovFull: yarn testCovPrepare && yarn testCovDev && yarn testCovProd && yarn testCovMin && yarn testCovReport
scripts.testCovNoMin: yarn testCovPrepare && yarn testCovDev && yarn testCovProd && yarn testCovReport
scripts.uglify: cross-env NODE_ENV=production envify lib/timm.js | uglifyjs - -o lib/timm.min.js --mangle --compress --comments "/^!/"
